title: Horse Power is Looking For players For Serious ranked 5s (Jungler, ADC or Support)
body:
We are Horse power, and we are looking for a Jungler, ADC or Support.
Add me if you where low diamond last season or this season.
Add e z if you would like to try out.

replies.body:
Can play any role, played in a lot of teams so know how 5's work ign Wolves
Happy to try out and if doesnt work than il leave with HONOR!!
The support role has been taken, we are just looking for a jangler now.

What other qualifications are needed?

I was D5 last season, I like to do the Support of the bottom lane with the help of using a champion.

(Also +10 points for two 'Yolo' names)
